CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Glen Burnie Bancorp is a bank holding company for The Bank of Glen Burnie. It offers retail and commercial banking services such as checking, savings, loans, mobile banking, online banking, wire transfer, ACH services, debit card, automated teller machines, and safe deposit boxes among others. The bank generates its revenue in the form of interest income. All of the revenues are earned within the United States.
